---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy | Lift and Measure';
const description = 'How Lift and Measure uses cookies, Google AdSense, and analytics, explained in plain language.';
const path = '/privacy-policy';
const lastUpdated = 'July 7, 2026';

const schema = {
  '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
  itemListElement: [
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://liftandmeasure.com' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Privacy Policy', item: 'https://liftandmeasure.com/privacy-policy' },
  ],
};
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} path={path} schema={schema}>
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="sep">&gt;</span>
    <span aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</span>
  </nav>

  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="disclaimer">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

  <p>
    This page explains what data Lift and Measure collects, why, and how you can control it. We
    have kept it in plain language rather than dense legal text.
  </p>

  <h2>What This Site Does Not Do</h2>
  <p>
    Every calculator on this site runs entirely in your browser. Values you type into a tool,
    like your body weight, age, or lift totals, are never sent to a server, stored in a database,
    or seen by anyone else. There is no account system and nothing to sign up for.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    This site uses cookies for two purposes: to remember whether you have accepted or declined
    the cookie notice, and to support the advertising described below. Your browser lets you
    block or delete cookies at any time through its settings, though doing so may cause the
    cookie banner to reappear on your next visit.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Advertising and Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    This site uses Google AdSense to show ads. Google AdSense and its advertising partners use
    cookies to serve ads based on a visitor's prior visits to this site and to other sites across
    the web. This is sometimes called interest based or personalized advertising. It works by
    tracking browsing patterns at the browser or device level, not by identifying who you are.
  </p>
  <p>
    This advertising data does not include personal identifiers such as your name, home address,
    or email address. Google's own explanation of how it and its partners handle data collected
    on sites like this one is available at
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Visitors in the European Economic Area and the United Kingdom are shown a consent banner that
    lets them choose whether to allow personalized advertising, in line with Google's certified
    consent requirements for those regions.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you would prefer not to see personalized ads, you can adjust your settings directly with
    Google at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a>,
    or use the industry wide opt-out tool provided by the Digital Advertising Alliance at
    <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info</a>.
    Both let you opt out of interest based advertising across many participating sites and
    advertisers, not just this one.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can also disable cookies entirely through your browser's settings, which applies to the
    cookies used for advertising as well as the ones this site uses to remember your cookie
    banner choice. Doing so may cause some site features, such as remembering that choice between
    visits, to stop working as expected.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    This site may use a privacy-conscious analytics tool to understand overall traffic, such as
    which pages are visited and roughly how many people visit, so the site can be improved. Any
    analytics used here does not identify you personally and is separate from the advertising
    cookies described above.
  </p>

  <h2>Health and Fitness Information</h2>
  <p>
    The calculators on this site work with figures like body weight, body fat percentage, heart
    rate, and calorie targets. As explained above, none of this information is transmitted
    anywhere or stored outside your own browser. This site does not provide medical advice, and
    the results are for general informational purposes only. See the
    <a href="/terms">Terms of Use</a> for more on that point.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    This site is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect personal
    information from them.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this page with a new "last
    updated" date at the top.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this policy can be sent to
    <a href="mailto:contact@liftandmeasure.com">contact@liftandmeasure.com</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
